para_trans: Reference: - Government Decision, No.-Shaniva-1520 / Q. 15/23 -A, D. January 09, 2020
Hon'ble Smt. Sunetra Ajit Pawar, Hon'ble Minister of State for Maharashtra, Shri. The Deputy Chief Minister was given the charge of "Devagiri," Malabar Hill,
The government has decided to allot a government bungalow in Mumbai.
2. Allotment to the Hon'ble Minister after he demits office, as provided in the relevant Government Decision.
The accommodation made shall be compulsorily vacated within a period of fifteen days.
3. To make the said Government Decision available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
